  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Like an archon's aura, the light of your thrown weapons can shake even the fiercest of foes.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Lantern Light, Lantern Style, Point-Blank Shot, Precise Shot, good or lawful alignment, caster level 11th or monk level 11th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Creatures you hit with a thrown weapon as well as creatures within 20 feet of your target must succeed at a Will save (DC = 10 + half your character level + your Charisma modifier) or become shaken until they damage you or 24 hours have passed. A creature that succeeds at its saving throw or that damages you after becoming shaken becomes immune to this effect for 24 hours.",
